Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Sought-after 60m2 in the heart of it all

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
A perfectly-sized, approx. 60sqm retail space has become available along Milligan Street, between the busy Hay and Murray Streets at the west end of the Perth CBD.

Surrounded by large office buildings such as QV1, hospitality including The Melbourne Hotel and RAC Arena as well as an abundance of thriving local and national retail, this location presents an exciting opportunity for Food & Beverage, Service and Specialty retail.

With air conditioning, a toilet, hot water and drainage in situ, setting up shop in this tenancy will be a breeze. The tenant here will enjoy huge exposure to heavy passing traffic and high daily footfall.

Don't miss out - book an inspection with the CBRE leasing team today.
